emailcontent.subject: re:Order now and don't forget about a discount

body.content:
Dear valued member.

This letter is a part of the official program initiated by the United American Health Department  please, read it to the end if you regularly buy drugs on the Web.

There are so many online drugstores on the Web today  but not all of them are as reliable as one might want them to be. Actually, only a few of them (for example, USDrugs) sell 100% generic meds  so you have to be really careful while choosing where to buy your pills.

Please, dont be indifferent to the questions of your own health  choose qualitative meds!

--
If you have any more questions please contact to me.
Please include all previous messages in your email's.
-------------------------------------------
Thank you and best regards
Nanette Burt
Email: 42stocknews@towersemi.com
WWW: http://mcebie.perfectblues.hk/?jsuegmghywzf
